{"tid":611701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解普遍香港人都有呢一樣共通點？","createTime":"2018-03-31T09:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T10:19:58.000Z","uid":28991,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8e47471662deb8362b53d80b93488b816c9858db","tid":611701,"uid":28991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T09:45:07.000Z","msg":"想講好耐，我諗我都唔係第一個提出呢樣嘢，但係真係一直都唔明點解香港有種咁嘅風氣，就係無論任何人做任何野都會比人屌，即使係一件好事啲人都係鍾意係雞蛋裏面挑骨頭，咩都唔滿意，點都要搵啲嘢黎屌一餐。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例如，<br />\n平胸又俾人話飛機場，大波嘅又比人話P圖sip嘢墊大個波，露肉就比人話姣係雞係公廁，走韓風又比人話偽韓仔偽韓妹，Abc又會話偽Abc扮上菜，mk又會屌話死mk仔mk妹，肥又話太油膩，瘦又話營養不良，成功少少就比人話拉關係靠上位......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實點解會咁？我諗左好耐都R曬頭，我睇外國啲人都唔係咁？咁嗰啲成日着着住比堅尼好性感嗰啲鬼妹係咪全部都係雞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人同我一樣好迷惘。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d484d4ba89c26724dd796063511c60438da404b6","tid":611701,"uid":131122,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T09:46:29.000Z","msg":"我地鐘意踩低人黎提高自豪感"},{"pid":"2942541fe378b4b25b629ab7dda4bc6ee5365133","tid":611701,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T09:49:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8dad4aa250859d5628195c06f56112b4bb99818d","tid":611701,"uid":28991,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d484d4ba89c26724dd796063511c60438da404b6","tid":611701,"uid":131122,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T09:46:29.000Z","msg":"我地鐘意踩低人黎提高自豪感"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T09:49:57.000Z","msg":"其實好無謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家互相稱讚大家多啲唔好咩，成個社會都會開心啲，我諗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" c